<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[٦]</span> وَإِبَاحَتُهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيَجِبُ مَسْحُ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- أَكْثَرِ دَوَائِرِ عِمَامَةٍ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>- وَأَكْثَرِ ظَاهِرِ قَدَمِ خُفٍّ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- وَجَمِيعِ جَبِيرَةٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>- وَإِنْ ظَهَرَ بَعْضُ مَحَلِّ فَرْضٍ،<span class="c5"> أَوْ تَمَّتِ المُدَّةُ:</span> اسْتَأْنَفَ الطَّهَارَةَ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>-<span class="c5"> نَوَاقِضُ الوُضُوءِ ثَمَانِيَةٌ:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> خَارِجٌ مِنْ سَبِيلٍ مُطْلَقاً.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَخَارِجٌ مِنْ بَقِيَّةِ البَدَنِ مِنْ بَوْلٍ، وَغَائِطٍ، وَكَثِيرٍ نَجِسٍ غَيْرِهِمَا.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> وَزَوَالُ عَقْلٍ، إِلَّا يَسِيرَ نَوْمٍ مِنْ قَائِمٍ أَوْ قَاعِدٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c4">[٤]</span> وَغُسْلُ مَيِّتٍ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c4">[٥]</span> وَأَكْلُ لَحْمِ إِبِلٍ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c4">[٦]</span> وَالرِّدَّةُ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>- وَكُلُّ مَا أَوْجَبَ غُسْلاً غَيْرَ مَوْتٍ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>